<h2 id='search-events'>Search Events</h2>
<p>This endpoint allows for events to be listed across all charities.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>http GET example.com/api/TBD?id_province<span class="o">=</span>3&amp;tag<span class="o">=</span>5&amp;offset<span class="o">=</span>0&amp;limit<span class="o">=</span>10
</code></pre></div><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code><span class="nx">TODO</span>
</code></pre></div><h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET example.com/api/TBD?id_province=3&amp;tag=5&amp;offset=0&amp;limit=10</code></p>
<h3 id='parameters'>Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>id_province</td>
<td>The province to filter by</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>tag</td>
<td>The tag/category to filter by</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>offset</td>
<td>The starting record (for pagination)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>limit</td>
<td>The number of records to return</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<blockquote>
<p>The above command returns JSON structured like this:</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
